# Training Marketplace

## Baseline Requirements (MVP1)
1. Marketplace for Trainers across the Globle
2. The website should support multi-currency for accepting payment(s)
3. Should be able to support mutiple timezones
4. Trainers should be able to create the course and schedule it as per their timezones
5. Students should be able to enroll to the course
6. Trainers should be able to view all the students, without any "special coins"
7. Trainers should be able to provide trainings
8. Students should be able to rate/review each trainings

## Ehnacements (MVP2)
1. Trainers should be able to provide assignment to their students
2. Trainers can view enrollments by using "special coins"

